  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01700:3b98a5fde0ac]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01701:6b42311eddbd]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01702:ff2eb9e78880]]{remark}\n做题时最容易错的一步，是把[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01703:396debc87988]]和[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01704:79383810359e]]混为一谈。真正长期留下来的，是外界逼出来的频率 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01705:401e4ca764fd]]；系统自己的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01706:8e6c503c1f3c]] 则藏在振幅和相位如何随 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01707:401e4ca764fd]] 变化这件事里。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01708:06b3847e1b6f]]{remark}\n",
