  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01709:c1d88f77fbb0]]",
  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01691:1d6a60d17fe0]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01692:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n阻尼很弱，先算无阻尼固有角频率和衰减系数：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01693:6dad971635da]]\n弱阻尼下 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01694:a68a4080449a]]，振动频率几乎不变。振幅 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01695:72d87f14ff3e]]，衰减到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01696:8a3566bccb08]] 时 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01697:daeb8260c5cf]]，即 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01698:dc49e080164c]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01699:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
